Description: KDE Plasma widget to cast media to Chromecast devices
 KCast is a KDE Plasma widget (Plasmoid) that lets you cast media from your
 desktop to Chromecast devices via the 'catt' backend. This package contains
 the widget and its QML/C++ plugin.
